{"type":null,"faqId":37082,"title":"手环放耳朵上或者手插口袋里走路会计步吗？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手环放在耳朵上步行时会计步，因为华为手环用的是业界最先进的六轴传感器。建议步行和跑步的时候，还是将手环放到腕带上，数据会更准确，而蓝牙在耳朵上容易丢失：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果放在口袋中，环境是比较复杂的，因为在口袋中运动，手环的翻动无规律，是不能很好的统计步数。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2246","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":75,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,计步,记录运动,手插口袋,手环放耳朵","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}